MAD's eighth annual review of the dumbest people, events and things of the year takes aim at Tom Cruise, Kevin Federline, Brajelina, the Runaway Bride, Dave Chappelle, Kate Moss, Rafael Palmeiro, Lil' Kim, Paula Abdul and many more! Plus, MAD plays Scrooge with the 25 Worst Things About Christmas!
